response.original_title: NJPW The New Beginning In Osaka 2018
response.overview: The New Beginning in Osaka (2018) was professional wrestling event promoted by New Japan Pro Wrestling (NJPW). The event took place on February 10, 2018, in Osaka, Osaka, at Edion Arena Osaka. The event featured nine matches, three of which were contested for championships. In the main event, Kazuchika Okada defended the IWGP Heavyweight Championship against SANADA. This was the fourteenth event under the New Beginning name and the fifth under the New Beginning in Osaka name.
response.title: NJPW The New Beginning In Osaka 2018
